---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const LAST_UPDATED = 'July 4, 2026';
const CONTACT_EMAIL = 'info@tokyoinseason.com';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="Disclaimer for Tokyo in Season: information accuracy, pricing, booking responsibility, and affiliate relationships."
  ogType="website"
>
  <h1 class="font-serif font-semibold text-4xl text-sumi mb-2 leading-tight">Disclaimer</h1>
  <p class="text-warm-gray-mid text-sm mb-12">Last updated {LAST_UPDATED}</p>

  <div class="prose max-w-none text-sumi leading-relaxed space-y-6">

    <h2 class="font-serif font-semibold text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Information accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      Tokyo in Season publishes prices, availability, schedules, and descriptions of tea ceremony
      and other cultural experiences as a reference. We check listings regularly and note when
      each page was last updated, but providers change their prices, hours, and offerings without
      notice, and we cannot guarantee that everything on this site is current or error-free at the
      moment you read it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif font-semibold text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Always verify before booking</h2>
    <p>
      Before you book or pay for any experience mentioned on this site, confirm the current price,
      availability, and details directly with the provider or booking platform. Treat everything
      here as a starting point for your own research, not a substitute for it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif font-semibold text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">We are not a party to your booking</h2>
    <p>
      Tokyo in Season is an independent review and comparison site. We do not sell tickets, take
      payments, or operate any of the experiences we write about. When you book through a link on
      this site, your contract is with the booking platform (such as GetYourGuide or Klook) or the
      experience provider directly — not with us. Any dispute about a booking, cancellation,
      refund, or the experience itself should be directed to the provider or platform you booked
      through.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif font-semibold text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Affiliate relationships</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links, including links to GetYourGuide and Klook. If
      you click one of these links and make a booking, we may earn a small commission at no extra
      cost to you. This does not influence our practitioner ratings or editorial opinions — we
      rate every experience the way we would recommend it to a friend, regardless of whether it
      pays a commission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-serif font-semibold text-2xl text-sumi mt-10 mb-4 not-prose">Questions</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this disclaimer, contact us at{' '}
      <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`} class="text-matcha underline">{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.
    </p>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-warm-gray">
    <p class="text-sm">
      <a href="/privacy" class="text-matcha hover:underline">Privacy Policy →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
